# 🚧 Traffic Safety Center

A production-ready website for a traffic safety business, focused on service presentation, client communication, and accessibility.

🌐 Live Website: https://www.trafficsafetycenter.com

---

## 🧠 Overview

This version of the project represents the initial stage of the system — a fully functional business website before the addition of an e-commerce store.

The goal was to create a clean, professional, and accessible platform for presenting services and enabling fast client communication.

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

**Frontend**
- HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
- Bootstrap (RTL support)

**Backend**
- Node.js
- Express

**Other Tools**
- Telegram Bot API (contact integration)
- Render (deployment)

---

## ⚙️ Features

### 🛣️ Service Presentation
- Structured service pages (road marking, signage, traffic arrangements)
- Clean UI focused on clarity and professionalism

### 📩 Contact System
- Contact form connected to Telegram
- Real-time message delivery to business owner

### 📱 Responsive Design
- Fully responsive across mobile, tablet, and desktop
- RTL support for Hebrew

### ♿ Accessibility
- Built according to Israeli Standard (T"י 5568) / WCAG AA principles
- Includes:
  - Text scaling
  - High contrast mode
  - Animation disabling
  - Readable fonts

---

